response.original_title: Skyhooks - Right There On My DVD
response.overview: This is the story of Skyhooks, one of the greatest bands in Australian music history. With 15 video clips all digitally re-mastered plus live and never before seen footage, a full interactive discography and stunning photo gallery, "Right There On My DVD" takes an in-depth look at perhaps one of the most influential bands of a generation.
response.title: Skyhooks - Right There On My DVD
